{"tid":923043,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利迷幫兩難民偷渡英國 還擁抱合照","createTime":"2018-12-01T02:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T14:11:14.000Z","uid":147522,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2d97b1b1c6f4768fcd20e157ca36f3145e989c42","tid":923043,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:03:02.000Z","msg":"　在週中的歐聯比賽，利物浦作客1-2負於巴黎聖日耳門。而賽後利物浦球迷返回英國時，還帶上了兩位偷渡的難民。<br />\n<br />\n      利物浦球迷們在看望作客的歐聯比賽後，乘坐大巴回國。但在大巴車開到倫敦的M25高速公路時，發現車內有兩名試圖偷渡到英國的難民，其中一人冒著生命危險藏在車底下，另一人藏在發動機艙內。<br />\n　　不過利物浦球迷們對待這兩名偷渡者非常友好，紛紛和兩人擁抱合照，並且還把照片發到社交媒體上。而利物浦球迷們這種「友善」對待難民的舉動得到了歐美網民的一致好評。而大巴車所在的旅遊公司發言人也表示，「迎接這兩人的第一件事就是友好的微笑、握手和擁抱，大家都很歡迎他們。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2oU8hi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2oU8hi.png&h=774a5583&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c24bd9eb350672bd627bc45179c68baa93ce859","tid":923043,"uid":77355,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:04:56.000Z","msg":"垃圾猁"},{"pid":"665e7c5558de49497d54bafc99943271b26fc11b","tid":923043,"uid":17910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:06:02.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c6a4afabe3b43ed0270c4d3967db0a854c44982c","tid":923043,"uid":147522,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:06:37.000Z","msg":"好似m記圖"},{"pid":"2cae98b068e45e44d83f454d799b93f8e3647785","tid":923043,"uid":224787,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:07:10.000Z","msg":"引狼入室，垃圾猁"},{"pid":"1669420f603d1415a134c831741a1799ae5821a2","tid":923043,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:17:26.000Z","msg":"利迷好人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc64b8a474ac1c778391b8ebb7d6c19d0b1d0a70","tid":923043,"uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1669420f603d1415a134c831741a1799ae5821a2","tid":923043,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"